Use this extension 
```
extension StringEllipsis on String {
  String tight() {
    return Characters(this)
        .replaceAll(Characters(' '), Characters('\u{000A0}'))
        .toString();
  }
}
```
then use it as the following
```
Row(
         children: [
                              Flexible(
                                child: Text(
                                 value.tight(),
                                  maxLines: 1,
                                  overflow: TextOverflow.ellipsis,
                                ),
                              ),
                         ],
 ),

```

